// A generator that does basically nothing.
// Like sqrt.evc, it's my hillbilly duct-table n' WD-40 way to
// benchmark EvilCandy right now, by comparing below with
// an equivalent algorithm in Python.  In two phrases,
// Python is faster but this is still pretty fast.
((generator_call) => {
    for x in generator_call(100 * 1000* 1000)
        ;
})((x) => {
    for i in range(x)
        yield i;
});

